    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. When you say hair should be \"neatly styled and conservative,\" what kind of specific looks or styles are you thinking of? I want to be able to give them concrete examples of what works and what might be seen as too casual or unprofessional for a boardroom environment.",
